    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 10pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.38; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Dans le monde des entreprises, un business model est un document synth&eacute;tique qui d&eacute;crit la situation &eacute;conomique d&#39;une soci&eacute;t&eacute;. Il apporte des pr&eacute;cisions sur le positionnement de l&#39;entreprise, sur ses activit&eacute;s, sur les moyens mis en &oelig;uvre et sur les ressources dont elle dispose pour atteindre ses objectifs.</span><span is="qowt-line-break"><br></span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Le business model d&eacute;crit &eacute;galement les principes de fonctionnement ainsi que les r&egrave;gles d&#39;organisation d&#39;une entreprise.</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 24.75pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Parmi les objectifs du Business Model&nbsp;:</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-24_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-22-0 1; counter-reset: lc-22-1 0 lc-22-2 0 lc-22-3 0 lc-22-4 0 lc-22-5 0 lc-22-6 0 lc-22-7 0 lc-22-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Il permet d&#39;identifier vos intentions et vos objectifs</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-24_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-22-0 1; counter-reset: lc-22-1 0 lc-22-2 0 lc-22-3 0 lc-22-4 0 lc-22-5 0 lc-22-6 0 lc-22-7 0 lc-22-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Il permet de d&eacute;crire votre strat&eacute;gie ainsi que les mesures mises en place pour parvenir &agrave; atteindre vos buts</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-24_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-22-0 1; counter-reset: lc-22-1 0 lc-22-2 0 lc-22-3 0 lc-22-4 0 lc-22-5 0 lc-22-6 0 lc-22-7 0 lc-22-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Il sert &eacute;galement &agrave; positionner votre entreprise dans le cadre de la situation concurrentielle actuelle et future</span></p>
