    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 13.5pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-decoration: underline;">ERREURS &Agrave; &Eacute;VITER</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Il ne faut pas&nbsp;:</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-14_1 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 72pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-1 1; counter-reset: lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">D&eacute;passer les 2 pages</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;afin de vouloir mettre plus d&#39;information. Il est &eacute;vident que nous ne pouvons pas tout &nbsp;citer en deux pages, mais le but du r&eacute;sum&eacute; est &nbsp;de donner envie de lire la suite&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-14_1 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 72pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-1 1; counter-reset: lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">Commercialiser votre produit ou service</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp; Le r&eacute;sum&eacute; n&#39;est pas destin&eacute; &agrave; vos clients, mais &agrave; vos investisseurs. Il ne s&#39;agit donc pas de vendre un produit ou un service mais votre projet et votre &eacute;quipe en deux pages</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-14_1 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 72pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-1 1; counter-reset: lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">Survendre</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;: Le r&eacute;sum&eacute; doit donner envie sans tomber dans un exc&egrave;s de subjectivit&eacute; (souligner les points forts tout en restant r&eacute;aliste)</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-14_1 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 72pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-1 1; counter-reset: lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">Oublier&nbsp;de demander pourquoi on veut un rendez-vous</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;: Si vous r&eacute;digez un r&eacute;sum&eacute; et un business plan, c&#39;est dans le but d&#39;obtenir quelque chose : un rendez-vous, un financement, une incubation etc. D&egrave;s lors, il faut indiquer pourquoi vous contactez votre interlocuteur, en fin du r&eacute;sum&eacute;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-14_1 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px -14.15pt 0px 72pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-1 1; counter-reset: lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">Oublier l&#39;&eacute;quipe</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;: Si le r&eacute;sum&eacute; sert &agrave; vendre le projet, il sert &eacute;galement &agrave; vendre vos ressources humaines donc votre &eacute;quipe. On doit d&eacute;celer, d&egrave;s le r&eacute;sum&eacute;, que votre &eacute;quipe est la bonne pour mener &agrave; bien le projet</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">&Eacute;TUDE DE MARCH&Eacute;</span></p>
</div>
<div style="position: absolute; pointer-events: none; margin: 70.85pt 42.45pt 70.85pt 70.85pt; top: 0px; right: 0px; width: 482pt; height: 700.2pt;"><br></div>
<div style="-webkit-box-flex: 1; padding-left: 70pt; padding-right: 42pt;">
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;&eacute;tude de march&eacute; est une &eacute;tape cruciale dont l&rsquo;objectif est de valider l&rsquo;existence d&rsquo;une opportunit&eacute; de march&eacute;. Il vous faudra expliciter les &eacute;l&eacute;ments suivants&nbsp;:</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-21_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-2-0 1; counter-reset: lc-2-1 0 lc-2-2 0 lc-2-3 0 lc-2-4 0 lc-2-5 0 lc-2-6 0 lc-2-7 0 lc-2-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;&eacute;tat du march&eacute;&nbsp;: En croissance ou non ?&nbsp;Pourquoi ?&nbsp;Sur quel segment ?</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-21_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-2-0 1; counter-reset: lc-2-1 0 lc-2-2 0 lc-2-3 0 lc-2-4 0 lc-2-5 0 lc-2-6 0 lc-2-7 0 lc-2-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Les changements r&eacute;cents du march&eacute;&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-21_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-2-0 1; counter-reset: lc-2-1 0 lc-2-2 0 lc-2-3 0 lc-2-4 0 lc-2-5 0 lc-2-6 0 lc-2-7 0 lc-2-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Les segments de clients&nbsp;: cr&eacute;ez des portraits concrets, expliquez vos crit&egrave;res de choix quant aux segments vis&eacute;s (vos niches), leurs habitudes d&rsquo;achats, de paiement, &hellip;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-21_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-2-0 1; counter-reset: lc-2-1 0 lc-2-2 0 lc-2-3 0 lc-2-4 0 lc-2-5 0 lc-2-6 0 lc-2-7 0 lc-2-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;&eacute;valuation de la taille du march&eacute;&nbsp;: en nombre de clients, chiffre d&rsquo;affaires potentiel</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-21_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-2-0 1; counter-reset: lc-2-1 0 lc-2-2 0 lc-2-3 0 lc-2-4 0 lc-2-5 0 lc-2-6 0 lc-2-7 0 lc-2-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;&eacute;tude de la concurrence&nbsp;: Vous devez &ecirc;tre en mesure d&rsquo;identifier vos concurrents, directs et indirects offrant des produits ou service de substitution</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Il faut r&eacute;ussir &agrave; vous d&eacute;marquer pour pouvoir exister et perdurer dans le temps. Vous serez donc amen&eacute; &agrave; vous positionner afin de d&eacute;jouer les strat&eacute;gies de vos rivaux. L&rsquo;analyse des acteurs pr&eacute;sents sur votre march&eacute; vous permettra d</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">&rsquo;</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">identifier vos forces, vos faiblesses et d&rsquo;anticiper d&rsquo;&eacute;ventuelles menaces</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">.</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;Cette &eacute;tude pr&eacute;alable &agrave; la cr&eacute;ation sera pour vous un moyen de comprendre ce qui vous diff&eacute;rencie des autres, du point de vue du client, et vous donnera donc un avantage consid&eacute;rable sur ces derniers.</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">La d&eacute;marche expos&eacute;e ci-apr&egrave;s vous aidera &agrave; mesurer la faisabilit&eacute; du projet</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">RECHERCHE DOCUMENTAIRE&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">March&eacute; : taille, taux de croissance, client&egrave;le</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Concurrence directe et indirecte&nbsp;:&nbsp;L&rsquo;analyse concurrentielle sert &agrave; d&eacute;montrer votre expertise de l&rsquo;activit&eacute; et de l&rsquo;environnement dans lequel votre future entreprise &eacute;voluera</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">.&nbsp;</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Ces informations int&eacute;resseront les investisseurs recherchant le meilleur placement &nbsp;en minimisant les risques de perte &eacute;ventuels. Une analyse concurrentielle de qualit&eacute; permettra de rassurer vos futurs partenaires et renforcera le caract&egrave;re professionnel de votre projet</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold;">-&nbsp;</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cartographier les acteurs et produits pouvant &ecirc;tre jug&eacute;s comme &laquo;mena&ccedil;ants&nbsp;&raquo; pour votre projet</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Identifier les leaders&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- D&eacute;nombrer les concurrents directs et indirects&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Caract&eacute;riser les entreprises qui r&eacute;ussissent</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Rechercher les donn&eacute;es financi&egrave;res basiques de vos concurrents (CA, marge, &hellip;)</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><br></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-2_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-23-0 1; counter-reset: lc-23-1 0 lc-23-2 0 lc-23-3 0 lc-23-4 0 lc-23-5 0 lc-23-6 0 lc-23-7 0 lc-23-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Fournisseurs : D&eacute;nombrer les fournisseurs potentiels et&nbsp;</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">benchmarker</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;leurs prix</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-2_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-23-0 1; counter-reset: lc-23-1 0 lc-23-2 0 lc-23-3 0 lc-23-4 0 lc-23-5 0 lc-23-6 0 lc-23-7 0 lc-23-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Distribution : Identifier les modes, les&nbsp;circuits et les co&ucirc;ts de distribution</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-2_0 qowt-list qowt-stl-NoSpacing" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-23-0 1; counter-reset: lc-23-1 0 lc-23-2 0 lc-23-3 0 lc-23-4 0 lc-23-5 0 lc-23-6 0 lc-23-7 0 lc-23-8 0;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">R&eacute;glementation : conna&icirc;tre et ma&icirc;triser le cadre juridique de votre offre&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 13.5pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(239, 61, 37);">&Eacute;TUDE TERRAIN</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 13.5pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;&eacute;tude terrain est un moyen efficace pour tester votre offre et conna&icirc;tre les attentes de votre future client&egrave;le. L&rsquo;objectif est de recueillir un maximum de feedbacks pour adapter votre offre ou votre strat&eacute;gie de Mix Marketing &agrave; votre cible.&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-20_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 6.75pt; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-3-0 1; counter-reset: lc-3-1 0 lc-3-2 0 lc-3-3 0 lc-3-4 0 lc-3-5 0 lc-3-6 0 lc-3-7 0 lc-3-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">L&rsquo;Etude qualitative</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: underline;">- Les entretiens en face &agrave; face</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;: Cette pratique consiste &agrave; interviewer vos clients potentiels individuellement sur la base d&rsquo;un guide d&rsquo;entretien pr&eacute;alablement pr&eacute;par&eacute;. L&rsquo;objectif est de comprendre leurs habitudes, leurs comportements d&#39;achat et leur sentiment vis-&agrave;-vis de votre probl&eacute;matique. Ils permettent d&rsquo;aborder en d&eacute;tail les th&eacute;matiques propres &agrave; votre projet, et de rebondir sur les aspects qui vous semblent les plus pertinents.&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration: underline;">- Les focus groups</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;: Ils consistent &agrave; interroger un groupe de personnes r&eacute;unies pour l&rsquo;occasion. Dans cette pratique, c&#39;est &eacute;galement vous qui dirigez la s&eacute;ance. Le d&eacute;roulement de la s&eacute;ance, les th&egrave;mes abord&eacute;s et les objectifs doivent &ecirc;tre minutieusement pr&eacute;par&eacute;s et d&eacute;finis au pr&eacute;alable. Les individus sond&eacute;s peuvent interagir, donner leurs avis et confronter leurs id&eacute;es. Veillez tout de m&ecirc;me &agrave; ne pas trop vous &eacute;loigner de votre probl&eacute;matique et pensez toujours &agrave; vos axes directeurs.&nbsp;</span></p>
